rect.aria-label: Speed vs. Trip of Time, , Scatter plot with 44 points. Use the arrow keys to navigate chart information and Tab to access the chart content.
X axisshows Total Trip Time (in Hours) and ranges from 0 to 22.
Y axisshows Miles per Hour and ranges from 0 to 140.
Legendshows Car Make and has values Audi, BMW, Chevorlet, Ford, Honda, Kia, Lexus, Subaru, Tesla, Toyota, and Volkswagon.
Chart Area with 11 series and 44 total points. To navigate the chart, press Enter to move into the list of points or Shift Tab to return to chart information.
